    {816,"Mighty Stomp",132368,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Throngus stomps his foot on the ground, triggering the walls of Grim Batol to Cave In. Throngus will not Mighty Stomp if he has his shield equipped.",-1,0,0,0,132,817,1,0,0},
    {817,"Cave In",132153,2,0,0,{"wago"},"After the Mighty Stomp of Throngus weakens the walls of Grim Batol, pieces of stone begin to fall on top of a random player in a $74986A1 yard radius area. Players who continue to stand in that area take $74986s1 Physical damage every second.",-1,0,0,0,132,818,2,0,0},
    {818,"Pick Weapon",134400,1,0,0,{"wago"},"Throngus has several fearsome weapons at his disposal. Periodically during the encounter, he randomly chooses between a massive Shield, a pair of Swords, or a punishing Mace. The chosen weapon grants him new abilities for a short duration of the encounter.",-1,0,0,0,132,819,3,0,0},
    {819,"Shield Abilities",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,820,0,0,132,823,4,0,0},
    {820,"Personal Phalanx",331053,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Throngus points his shield at a random player every 10 seconds. Damage dealt to Throngus by a player standing in front of the shield is reduced by $74909s1%.",-1,0,0,2,132,821,5,819,0},
    {821,"Flaming Arrow",132312,2,0,0,{"wago"},"While Throngus has a shield equipped, archers constantly fire flaming arrows from overhead windows at random players. Each flaming arrow inflicts $74944s1 Fire damage.",-1,0,0,0,132,822,6,819,0},
    {822,"Flaming Shield",134982,2,0,2,{"wago"},"A 60 degree cone of fire erupts forward from Throngus' shield, inflicting $90830s1 Fire damage every second to any enemy target engulfed by the fire.",-2,0,0,8,132,0,7,819,0},
    {823,"Swords Abilities",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,824,0,0,132,828,8,0,0},
    {824,"Dual Blades",132147,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Throngus wields a flaming sword in each hand, granting him the ability to attack simultaneously with each weapon. His melee damage is reduced by $74981s3% during this time.",-1,0,0,0,132,825,9,823,0},
    {825,"Thrash",132152,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Throngus will occasionally attack an additional two times when he swings his swords.",-1,0,0,0,132,826,10,823,0},
    {826,"Disorienting Roar",132352,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Throngus lets loose a tremendous roar, decreasing the attack and cast speeds of players by $74976s1%. Players may remove this effect by casting a spell or using an ability.  $[2,4\n\n\n\nIn Heroic Difficulty Disorienting Roar reduces attack and cast speeds of players by 150%, and each time a player casts a spell or uses an ability the amount of the reduction lowers by $74976s1%.$]",-1,0,0,0,132,827,11,823,0},
    {827,"Burning Flames",135822,2,0,2,{"wago"},"The fiery blades burn the target of Throngus' melee attacks, inflicting $90764s1 Fire damage every $90764t1 seconds for $90764d. This effect stacks, but a single dispel effect removes all stacks.",-2,0,0,140,132,0,12,823,0},
    {828,"Mace Abilities",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,829,0,0,132,0,13,0,0},
    {829,"Encumbered",133490,2,0,0,{"wago"},"The incredibly massive weight of Throngus' mace decreases his movement speed by $75007s2%, but increases his melee attack damage by $75007s1%.",-1,0,0,1,132,830,14,828,0},
    {830,"Impaling Slam",133490,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Throngus jumps to a random target, impaling them on his mace and inflicting $75056s3 Physical damage every $75056t3 second for $75056d.",-1,0,0,0,132,831,15,828,0},
    {831,"Lava Patch",135822,2,0,2,{"wago"},"As Throngus moves with his fiery mace, he leaves patches of fire on the ground. These patches deal $90754s1 Fire damage every second to any player who stands in them.",-2,0,0,8,132,0,16,828,0},
    {2010,"Stage One: Fists of Flame and Frost",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,2011,0,0,89,2014,1,0,0},
    {2011,"Fists of Flame",135817,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Glubtok shrouds his fists in flame, causing each of his melee attacks that land to deal $87874s1 Fire damage.\n\n\n\nAdditionally, when Glubtok lands a melee attack he will sometimes deal $87896s1 Fire damage and knock up nearby enemies within $87896A1 yards.",-1,0,0,0,89,2012,2,2010,0},
    {2012,"Fists of Frost",135785,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Glubtok coats his fists with frost, causing each of his melee attacks that land to deal $87899s1 Frost damage.\n\n\n\nAdditionally, when Glubtok lands a melee attack he will sometimes deal $87901s1 Frost damage, reduce the movement speed by $87901s2%, reduce the frequency of melee and ranged attacks by $87901s3%, and increase the casting time by $87901s3% of nearby enemies within $87901A1 yards for $87901d.",-1,0,0,0,89,2013,3,2010,0},
    {2013,"Blink",135736,2,0,0,{"wago"},"After either Fists of Flame or Fists of Frost wears off, Glubtok will randomly teleport to a location nearby a random player.$[2,4\n\n\n\nIn Heroic Difficulty, when Glubtok casts the Blink spell, he resets the threat of all enemies to zero.$]",-1,0,0,0,89,0,4,2010,0},
    {2014,"Stage Two: Arcane Power!",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"At 50% health, Glubtok blinks to the center of the room and levitates in place. Glubtok then begins to cast Fire Blossom and Frost Blossom spells randomly throughout the room.",-1,2015,0,0,89,0,5,0,0},
    {2015,"Fire Blossom",135817,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Glubtok launches a Fire Blossom at a random location in the room that lands two seconds later. When the Fire Blossom lands, it knocks up and inflicts $88173s1 Fire damage to nearby enemies within $88173A1 yards.$[2,4\n\n\n\nIn Heroic Difficulty, wherever the spell lands, a Fire Blossom creature rises from the flames and begins to attack.$]",-1,2018,0,0,89,2016,6,2014,0},
    {2016,"Frost Blossom",135785,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Glubtok launches a Frost Blossom at a random location in the room that lands two seconds later. When the Frost Blossom lands, it deals $88177s1 Frost damage, reduces the movement speed by $88177s2%, reduces the frequency of melee and ranged attacks by $88177s3%, and increases the casting time by $88177s3% of nearby enemies within $88177A1 yards for $88177d.$[2,4\n\n\n\nIn Heroic Difficulty, wherever the spell lands a Frost Blossom creature forms from the ice and begins to attack.$]",-1,2019,0,0,89,2017,8,2014,0},
    {2017,"Fire Wall",135926,2,0,2,{"wago"},"After casting Arcane Power, Glubtok creates a single wall of fire that begins to slowly rotate around him. Players who do not avoid the Fire Wall take $91397s1 Fire damage every second.",-2,0,0,8,89,0,10,2014,0},
