    {2020,"Stage One: Bombs away!",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"Helix Gearbreaker leaps onto the back of the Lumbering Oaf, and begins to order the Oaf around while throwing out Sticky Bombs.",-1,2021,0,0,90,2026,1,0,0},
    {2021,"Sticky Bomb",136173,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Helix will periodically toss a Sticky Bomb onto the ground near a random player. After six seconds if the bomb detects a nearby player within one yard, the bomb explodes. A Sticky Bomb will also self destruct and explode if it is not triggered by a player after eighteen additional seconds. When a Sticky Bomb explodes, it knocks back and deals $88321s1 damage to enemy targets within $88321A1 yards.",-1,0,0,0,90,2022,2,2020,0},
    {2022,"Oaf Smash",132318,2,0,0,{"wago"},"The Lumbering Oaf will periodically grab a player and run to the farthest side of the room from the entrance. The Oaf then quickly runs and smashes into a wooden log on the other side of the room, knocking back and dealing 100 Physical damage to the player.$[2,4\n\n\n\nIn Heroic Difficulty, the impact of Oaf Smash instead inflicts $88300s2% of the target player's health in Physical damage. $]",-1,0,0,0,90,2023,3,2020,0},
    {2023,"Throw Helix",370769,2,0,0,{"wago"},"The Lumbering Oaf will take Helix from his back, and throw the goblin onto a random player's face for ten seconds. While Helix is attached, he punches the player with his normal melee attack.",-1,0,0,0,90,2024,4,2020,0},
    {2024,"Chest Bomb",133712,2,0,2,{"wago"},"When Helix leaps back onto the Lumbering Oaf after being attached to player, he leaves a Chest Bomb strapped to the player. After ten seconds, the Chest Bomb explodes. This explosion knocks the targeted player up very high, while dealing $88250s1 Fire damage to nearby player allies within $88250A1 yards.",-2,0,0,8,90,2025,5,2020,0},
    {2025,"Helix' Crew",0,1,0,2,{"wago"},"Four members of Helix' Crew appear above the players on an overhead log. Each crew member will periodically throw a Sticky Bomb onto the ground below near a random player.",-2,0,36379,8,90,0,6,2020,0},
    {2026,"Stage Two: I didn't need him!",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"After the Lumbering Oaf dies, Helix Gearbreaker is thrown to the ground. Helix then uses his Sticky Bomb ability more frequently.",-1,2027,0,0,90,0,7,0,0},
    {2027,"Leap",370769,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Helix will leap and attach himself to a player's face for ten seconds. Helix then immediately picks a new player and leaps on them. While Helix is attached, he punches the player with his normal melee attack.",-1,0,0,0,90,2028,8,2026,0},
    {2028,"Chest Bomb",133712,2,0,2,{"wago"},"When Helix leaps off from a player, he leaves a Chest Bomb strapped to that player. After ten seconds, the Chest Bomb explodes. This explosion knocks the targeted player up very high, while dealing $88250s1 Fire damage to nearby player allies within $88250A1 yards.",-2,0,0,8,90,2029,9,2026,0},
