    {2140,"Word of Shame",237555,2,0,2,{"wago"},"When Commander Springvale has three charges of Unholy Power, he can consume the charges and cast this spell on a random enemy player. Word of Shame deals $93852s1% of a player's maximum health as Shadow damage every $93852t1 seconds. The effect lasts until either the targeted player or Commander Springvale dies.",-14,0,0,8,98,2142,4,0,0},
