    {2145,"Mortal Strike",132355,2,0,2,{"wago"},"The Wailing Guardsman instantly attacks his enemy, inflicting $91801s1% of their normal weapon damage and leaving the enemy wounded. This mortal wound reduces the effectiveness of any healing on the target by $91801s2%.",-14,0,0,0,98,0,8,2142,0},
