    {2221,"Blight of Ozumat",132291,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Ozumat now constantly spits out blight into the room. Every player is inflicted with $83561s1 Shadow damage every second for $83561d. This effect stacks every second until the end of the encounter.",-1,0,0,4,104,0,18,2220,0},
