    {2654,"Blazing Heat",135805,2,0,0,{"wago"},"A Lava Scion inflicts a random player with Blazing Heat, causing the player to create a trail of Blazing Heat in their wake. Blazing Heat inflicts $99144s1 Fire damage every $99128t1 sec on players standing within the trail, and heals Sons of Flame within the trail for $99145s1% every $99128t1 sec.",-1,0,0,0,198,0,31,2653,0},
