    {2657,"Lava Wave",451169,2,0,0,{"wago"},"If a player touches a moving Lava Wave, the lava inflicts $98928s1 Fire damage, $98928s2 Fire damage every $98928t2 sec. for $98928d., and knocks the player back.",-1,0,0,128,198,0,34,2656,0},
