    {2659,"World in Flames",236228,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Ragnaros periodically casts Engulfing Flames on a random section of the platform every $100171t1 sec for $100171d.",12,0,0,8,198,2660,36,2655,0},
    {2660,"Summon Living Meteor",135821,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Ragnaros calls down an increasing number of Living Meteors. The Living Meteor's impact inflicts $99317s1 Fire damage to players within $99317A1 yards of the location.",-1,2661,0,0,198,3537,37,2655,0},
    {2661,"Living Meteor",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"The Living Meteor fixates on a random player and chases them.",-1,2662,38677,0,198,0,38,2660,0},
    {2662,"Meteor Impact",135821,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Any player within $99279A1 yards of a Living Meteor triggers a Meteor Impact, inflicting $99287s1 Fire damage to players within $99287A1 yards.",-1,0,0,16,198,2663,39,2661,0},
    {2663,"Combustible",132847,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Attacking a Living Meteor causes Combustion, knocking it back several yards from the attacking player. Triggering Combustion removes the Combustible effect for 5 seconds.",-1,2664,0,0,198,3528,40,2661,0},
    {2664,"Combustion",451164,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Attacking a Living Meteor causes Combustion, knocking it back several yards from the attacking player.$[5,6\n\n\n\nIn Heroic Difficulty Combustion inflicts $100271s1 Fire damage every second for $99303d on the triggering player. This effect stacks.$]",-1,0,0,0,198,0,41,2663,0},
    {2665,"Stage Four: The True Power of the Firelord!",0,0,0,3,{"wago"},"The Firelord unleashes his full power and is able to move freely around the platform. Players have the aid of powerful heroes of Azeroth to support them.",12,2680,0,8,198,0,44,0,0},
    {2666,"Chaos Bolt",236291,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Setesh casts Chaos Bolt at random players instead of performing a melee attack. Chaos Bolt inflicts $77069s1 unresistable damage to a random player.",-1,0,0,0,129,2667,1,0,0},
    {2667,"Reign of Chaos",136202,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Setesh summons small $77030A2 yard radius bubbles of void energy every $77023t1 second at the location of players and random spots in the room. After a bubble is summoned, it immediately begins to inflict $77030s2 unresistable damage every second to enemies. Each bubble lasts 5 seconds before it pops.",-1,0,0,0,129,2668,2,0,0},
    {2668,"Chaos Blast",236291,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Setesh throws a Chaos Blast at the location of a random player that is at least 15 yards away from Setesh. After 5 seconds the Chaos Blast lands at the targeted location, inflicting $76681s1 unresistable damage to any player within $76681A1 yards. The Chaos Blast leaves behind a $76684A1 yard radius void zone that inflicts $76684s1 unresistable damage every second to any player standing in the area.",-1,0,0,0,129,2669,3,0,0},
    {2669,"Seed of Chaos",136193,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Setesh creates a Seed of Chaos at a random location in his room that drops to the floor. Moving close to the seed causes it to explode, inflicting $76870s1 Shadow damage to all enemies within $76870A1 yards. Players within the explosion are also infused with chaos for $76870d. and inflict an additional $76874s1 unresistable damage when they land one of their hostile abilities or spells on a target. This additional damage can only occur once every 2 seconds.",-1,0,0,0,129,2670,4,0,0},
    {2670,"Summon Chaos Portal",136202,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Setesh channels onto a random location in the room, and opens up a Chaos Portal. When the portal opens, two Void Wurms appear. After another 12 seconds a Void Seeker appears, then after 15 seconds a Void sentinel appears. The Chaos Portal then closes.$[2,4\n\n\n\nIn Heroic Difficulty the Chaos Portal does not automatically close. Players must attack and destroy the portal to stop additional void creatures from entering the fight. When this Chaos Portal opens, a Void Sentinel appears then two Void Wurms appear six seconds later. In another ten seconds a Void Seeker appears. Then every 15 seconds the Chaos Portal is still alive, two Void Wurms or one Void Seeker appears.$]",-1,2671,0,32,129,0,5,0,0},
    {2671,"Void Sentinel",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"The Chaos Portal summons one of these very difficult to kill creatures at a time.",-1,2672,32349,0,129,2673,6,2670,0},
    {2672,"Void Barrier",237568,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Void Sentinels wrap themselves in a barrier, reducing the damage dealt to them by $76959s1%.",-1,0,0,0,129,2874,7,2671,0},
    {2673,"Void Seeker",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"The Chaos Portal summons one of these void creatures at a time.",-1,2674,18957,0,129,2675,9,2670,0},
    {2674,"Anti-Magic Prison",136121,2,0,0,{"wago"},"The Void Seeker channels and traps its current target within an Anti-Magic Prison, reducing their movement speed by $76903s3% and causing the target to become immune to all magical effects (including friendly healing) for $76903d.",-1,0,0,69,129,0,10,2673,0},
    {2675,"Void Wurm",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"The Chaos Portal summons two of these low health creatures at a time.",-1,0,19285,0,129,0,11,2670,0},
    {2678,"Splitting Blow",525025,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Ragnaros buries Sulfuras within the platform, inflicting $100455s1 Fire damage every $100456t1 second to players within $100455A1 yards and creating eight Sons of Flame that attempt to reach the mighty hammer.",-1,0,0,0,198,2637,10,2636,0},
    {2679,"Splitting Blow",525025,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Ragnaros buries Sulfuras within the platform, inflicting $100455s1 Fire damage every $100456t1 second to players within $100455A1 yards and creating eight Sons of Flame that attempt to reach the mighty hammer.",-1,0,0,0,198,2650,26,2649,0},
    {2680,"Superheated",512617,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Ragnaros unleashes his full power and becomes Superheated, inflicting $100594s1 Fire damage every $100593t1 sec. on all players and increasing the damage dealt by Superheated by $100594s2%. This effect stacks.",12,0,0,8,198,2681,45,2665,0},
    {2681,"Empower Sulfuras",515200,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Ragnaros channels his flames upon Sulfuras. After $100604d. of channeling, Sulfuras becomes Empowered and Ragnaros' melee attacks unleash the Flames of Sulfuras, inflicting $100630s1 Fire damage to all players.",12,2682,0,8,198,2683,46,2665,0},
    {2682,"Flames of Sulfuras",135818,2,0,2,{"wago"},"With Sulfuras empowered, Ragnaros' melee attacks unleash the Flames of Sulfuras, inflicting $100630s1 Fire damage to all players.",12,0,0,24,198,0,47,2681,0},
    {2683,"Dreadflame",236216,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Ragnaros stomps and creates a Dreadflame at two nearby locations. The Dreadflame multiplies rapidly and spreads across the platform. Dreadflame inflicts $100941s1 Fire damage and $100941s2 Fire damage every $100941t2 sec for $100941d if a player touches the fire.$[4,6\n\n\n\nIn 25 player raids, Ragnaros creates six Dreadflames.$]",12,0,0,8,198,2685,48,2665,0},
    {2685,"Cenarius",0,1,0,2,{"wago"},"Although the son of Malorne and Elune, the mighty demigod and druid patron Cenarius was cared for in his youth by the Dragon Aspect Ysera. \n\n\n\nCenarius supports the raid by using his powers over nature to freeze Living Meteors and reduce the damage caused when Ragnaros is Superheated.",12,2686,38532,8,198,2687,49,2665,0},
    {2686,"Breadth of Frost",464484,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Cenarius forms a Breadth of Frost at a nearby random location. Any Living Meteors that enter the Breadth of Frost freeze and take $100567s3% additional damage from players. Breadth of Frost grants immunity to Superheated damage and removes the Superheated debuff from players standing within the area.",12,0,0,8,198,0,50,2685,0},
    {2687,"Arch Druid Hamuul Runetotem",0,1,0,2,{"wago"},"Apart from being revered by his fellow tauren, the greathearted archdruid Hamuul Runetotem is also a celebrated leader of the Cenarion Circle. \n\n\n\nThe wise tauren assists the raid by harnessing nature's fury and causes roots to erupt from the ground to entrap Ragnaros.",12,2688,38534,8,198,2689,51,2665,0},
    {2688,"Entrapping Roots",136100,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Arch Druid Hamuul Runetotem forms Entrapping Roots at a nearby random location. If Ragnaros enters the area of the Entrapping Roots, he becomes stunned for $100653d and takes $100653s2% additional damage while stunned.",12,0,0,8,198,0,52,2687,0},
