    {2794,"Venom Withdrawal",132108,2,0,2,{"wago"},"After Bloodvenom completes, High Priest Venoxis suffers from Venom Withdrawal for $96653d. Venom Withdrawal stuns Venoxis causes him to take $96653s1% additional damage. Once Venom Withdrawal expires, Venoxis begins his stage one activities again.",-2,0,0,0,175,0,14,2792,0},
    {2795,"Whispers of Hethiss",136070,2,0,2,{"wago"},"High Priest Venoxis focuses a beam of poison on a random player, inflicting $96469s1 Nature damage every $96466t2 seconds.",-2,0,0,64,175,2796,4,2787,0},
