    {2815,"Lynx Flurry",132127,2,0,2,{"wago"},"The Spirit of the Lynx begins to flurry, reducing its damage dealt by $43290s1% but increasing attack speed by $43290s2%.  While under the effects of Lynx Flurry, the Spirit of the Lynx gains immuntiy to stuns, roots, snares, and other effects that cause loss of control.",-2,0,0,0,189,2816,12,2813,0},
