    {2820,"Stage One: I Will Burn You From the Sky!",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"Alysrazor flies around the arena, allowing her minions to corner her foes far below. She periodically flies through the center of the arena to claw at foes.",-1,2826,0,0,194,2821,3,0,0},
