    {2824,"Firestorm",237588,2,0,0,{"wago"},"At the beginning of the battle Alysrazor ascends into the sky, inflicting $99605s1 Fire damage to players and knocking them back. Alysrazor continues to inflict $99606s1 Fire damage to players every $99605t2 sec. for $99605d.",-1,0,0,0,194,2825,1,0,0},
