    {2826,"Blazing Claw",135811,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Alysrazor claws her way through the center of the arena, inflicting $99844s1 Physical damage to enemies in a $99844A1 yard long 90 degree cone every $99843t1 seconds. Each swipe also increases the Fire and Physical damage dealt to the target by $99844s2% for $99844d.",3,0,0,0,194,2841,4,2820,0},
