    {2832,"Alysra's Razor",236297,2,0,0,{"wago"},"If a player gains 25 stacks of Blazing Power, they gain Alysra's Razor. This increases the player's critical strike chance by $100029s1% for $100029d.",-1,0,0,0,194,2833,11,2830,0},
    {2833,"Incendiary Cloud",135818,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Alysrazor periodically creates an increasing number of Incendiary Clouds lasting for 3 seconds. Players that pass through the cloud suffer $99427s1 Fire damage every $99427d.$[5,6\n\n\n\nIn Heroic Difficulty, Alysrazor always creates three Incendiary Clouds.$]",-1,0,0,0,194,0,12,2830,0},
