    {2836,"Voracious Hatchling",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"Early in Stage 1, two Blazing Broodmothers drop off two Molten Eggs. After several seconds the eggs hatch into Voracious Hatchlings. Voracious Hatchlings throw a Tantrum if not fed Plump Lava Worms.",-1,2837,38372,1,194,2843,18,2820,0},
