    {2841,"Firestorm",237588,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Alysrazor faces the center of the arena and kicks up a powerful, fiery wind. After 5 seconds the arena is bathed in flames, inflicting $100745s1 Fire damage every $100744t1 seconds to all players within line of sight for $100744d.",12,0,0,8,194,2827,5,2820,0},
