    {2843,"Plump Lava Worm",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"During Stage 1, two sets of four Plump Lava Worms erupt from the molten ground. Players cannot attack Plump Lava Worms. Voracious Hatchlings near a Plump Lava Worm rush to devour it, becoming Satiated.",-1,2844,37993,1,194,2845,24,2820,0},
