    {2869,"Surge",236305,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Nalorakk charges the most distant enemy, inflicting $42402s2 Physical damage. In addition, Physical damage dealt to the target increases by $42402s3% for $42402d.",-2,0,0,0,187,0,3,2867,0},
