    {2898,"Pillar of Fire",135926,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Daakara summons a pillar of fire at a random player's location. The pillar inflicts $43217s1 Fire damage to enemies within $43217R1 yds. every $43218t1 sec. and persists for $43218d.",-2,0,0,0,191,0,25,2895,0},
    {2899,"Stage One: Welcome to the Great Show!",0,0,0,3,{"wago"},"Jin'do fights players alone, dropping Deadzones on the ground to protect himself and calling upon the Spirit of Hakkar to empower his weapon with shadow lightning.",-2,2900,0,0,185,2902,1,0,0},
    {2900,"Deadzone",136120,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Jin'do creates a field of deadened magic on the ground at his feet. All units in this field take $97170s1% less magic damage, but have their casting speed reduced by $101360s1%.",-2,0,0,0,185,2901,2,2899,0},
    {2901,"Shadows of Hakkar",135990,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Jin'do draws power from the Spirit of Hakkar to charge his weapon. For the next $97172d. his attacks unleash bursts of energy that chain to additional targets, inflicting $97173s1 Shadow damage. Each additional target in the chain takes 85% less damage.",-2,0,0,0,185,0,3,2899,0},
    {2902,"Stage Two: Spitting in the Face of a God",0,0,0,3,{"wago"},"Jin'do drags his enemies with him into the spirit world. He draws tremendous power from Hakkar's spirit, which is held captive by three large chains.",-2,2903,0,0,185,3345,4,0,0},
    {2903,"Shadow Spike",132843,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Jin'do hurls a bolt of shadow at a random player's location. The spike explodes when it hits the ground, inflicting $97161s1 Shadow damage to enemies within $97161a1 yards.",-2,0,0,0,185,2904,5,2902,0},
