    {2906,"Body Slam",236171,2,0,2,{"wago"},"The Gurubashi Spirit jumps to a random target's location, inflicting $97252s1 damage to all units and other objects within $97252A1 yards of that location and knocking them back. This attack leaves a Sundered Rift on the ground, increasing the damage taken by units and objects in the $97320A1 yard radius area by $97320s1% for 20 seconds.",-2,2907,0,0,185,0,8,2904,0},
    {2907,"Sunder Rift",136158,2,0,2,{"wago"},"The Gurubashi Spirit's Body Slam attack leaves a Sunder Rift on the ground, increasing the damage taken by units and objects in the area by $97320s1% for 20 seconds.",-2,0,0,0,185,0,9,2906,0},
    {2908,"Twisted Spirit",0,1,0,2,{"wago"},"Twisted Spirits swarm out of portals around the temple and attack players in increasing numbers. Twisted Spirits inflict Shadow damage when they attack. These creatures have very low health.",-2,0,25553,0,185,2909,10,2902,0},
