    {2910,"Brittle Barrier",135733,2,0,2,{"wago"},"A barrier of arcane energy protects Hakkar's Chains and grants them immunity to all attacks and spells. Nothing short of an enormous Gurubashi troll spirit performing a Body Slam can break the barrier.",-2,0,0,0,185,0,12,2909,0},
    {2911,"Concentration",236225,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Each player who engages Fandral on Heroic Difficulty gains a Concentration power bar. This bar fills over time, increasing damage and healing done by $98254s1% for every 25 Concentration up to 100. Players hit by a damaging attack or spell lose all Concentration.",12,0,0,8,197,2912,1,0,0},
    {2912,"Shapeshifting",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"$[3,5Fandral transforms into a Cat when his enemies are not clustered together or into a Scorpion when 7 or more of his enemies are clustered together.$]$[4,6Fandral transforms into a Cat when his enemies are not clustered together or into a Scorpion when 18 or more of his enemies are clustered together.$]\n\n\n\nOn every third transform, Fandral briefly pauses in Night Elf form.",-1,2913,0,0,197,0,2,0,0},
    {2913,"Cat Form",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"Fandral transforms into a Cat when his enemies are not clustered together.",-1,2914,38208,0,197,2918,3,2912,0},
    {2914,"Leaping Flames",459027,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Fandral leaps at an enemy, leaving behind a Spirit of the Flame. He lands in a blaze of glory, igniting the ground at his destination and causing it to burn enemy units for $98535s1 Fire damage every $98535t1 sec. for $98535d. This attack costs 100 energy.",-1,0,0,0,197,2915,4,2913,0},
    {2915,"Spirit of the Flame",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"These images of Fandral attack enemies until defeated.",-1,0,38222,0,197,2916,5,2913,0},
    {2916,"Adrenaline",458737,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Fandral gains a stack of Adrenaline each time he performs Leaping Flames. Adrenaline increases his energy regeneration rate by $97238s1% per application. Fandral loses all stacks of Adrenaline when he switches forms.",-1,0,0,0,197,2917,6,2913,0},
    {2917,"Fury",236310,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Fandral gains a stack of Fury each time he transforms into a Cat or Scorpion, increasing the damage of Leaping Flames and Flame Scythe by $97235s1% per application. This effect stacks.",-1,0,0,0,197,0,7,2913,0},
    {2918,"Scorpion Form",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"Fandral transforms into a Scorpion when 7 or more of his enemies are clustered together.$[4,6\n\n\n\nIn 25 player raids, Fandral transforms when 18 or more of his enemies are clustered together.$]",-1,2919,38174,0,197,2922,8,2912,0},
    {2919,"Flame Scythe",135811,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Fandral inflicts $98474s1 Fire damage to enemies in front of him. Damage is split equally among targets hit. This attack costs 100 energy.",-1,0,0,0,197,2920,9,2918,0},
    {2920,"Adrenaline",458737,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Fandral gains a stack of Adrenaline each time he performs Flame Scythe. Adrenaline increases his energy regeneration rate by $97238s1% per application. Fandral loses all stacks of Adrenaline when he switches forms.",-1,0,0,0,197,2921,10,2918,0},
    {2921,"Fury",236310,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Fandral gains a stack of Fury each time he transforms into a Cat or Scorpion, increasing the damage of Leaping Flames and Flame Scythe by $97235s1% per application. This effect stacks.",-1,0,0,0,197,0,11,2918,0},
    {2922,"Night Elf Form",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"When Fandral enters Night Elf form, he briefly envelops his enemies in a Fiery Cyclone and casts an additional spell.\n\n\n\nWhen switching from Cat form to Scorpion form, Fandral unleashes Searing Seeds.\n\n\n\nWhen switching from Scorpion form to Cat form, Fandral unleashes Burning Orbs.",-1,2923,38695,0,197,0,12,2912,0},
