    {2925,"Burning Orbs",451164,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Fandral summons several orbs around the room. Each orb attacks the nearest player, burning them for $98584s1 Fire damage every $98584t1 sec. This effect stacks.",-1,0,0,0,197,0,15,2922,0},
