    {3144,"Stage Three: BEHOLD YOUR DOOM!",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"Once either Arion or Terrastra reaches 25% health, the Councillors grow impatient and place all combatants in a stasis field. All four Councillors combine to form the Elementium Monstrosity, beginning the final phase of the encounter.",-1,3145,0,0,158,0,40,0,0},
