    {3146,"Electric Instability",136050,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Every $84526t1 sec. the Monstrosity zaps nearby players with electrical bolts for $84529s1 Nature damage. The electrical bolt chains to nearby players. The Elementium Monstrosity is an unstable creature and emanates increasing amounts of electrical energy over time. The increased energy causes the electrical bolts to strike an increasing number of targets.",-1,0,0,0,158,3147,42,3145,0},
