    {3156,"Flame's Orders",132847,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Cho'gall calls forth a Fire elemental and absorbs the elemental into his Twilight Hammer, empowering it with Flaming Destruction.$[5,6\n\n\n\nOn Heroic difficulty Cho'gall gains one additional stack of Flaming Destruction for each 10% health remaining on the elemental when it is absorbed.$]",-1,3157,0,0,167,3158,10,3154,0},
    {3157,"Flaming Destruction",135817,2,0,0,{"wago"},"While Flame's Orders empowers Cho'gall's hammer, his melee attacks inflict $81527s1 additional Fire damage to his current target and splashes molten fire that creates a burning Blaze nearby.",-1,3211,0,0,167,0,11,3156,0},
