    {3164,"Stage Two: Come, Infinite Night!",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"When Cho'gall reaches 25% health, he calls upon the full powers of the Old Gods. He absorbs the dark energies of any remaining Corrupting Adherents and pools of Spilled Blood of the Old God, then transforms himself into a twisted creature.",-1,3217,0,0,167,0,23,0,0},
