    {3218,"Corruption of the Old God",136118,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Cho'gall fills the room with tendrils of shadowy corruption, inflicting $82363s1 Shadow damage every $82361t1 sec to all players and gradually increasing their Corruption level. Players suffer $81701s1% additional damage from Corruption of the Old God for each point of their Corruption.",-1,0,0,0,167,3219,25,3164,0},
