    {3221,"Debilitating Beam",237297,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Debilitating Beam reduces a target's healing and damage done by $82411s2% and inflicts $82411s1 Shadow damage every $82411t1 sec for $82411d.$[5,6\n\n\n\nOn Heroic difficulty, Debilitating Beam also causes Corrupted Blood.$]",-1,0,0,66,167,0,28,3220,0},
    {3222,"Corruption: Accelerated",136118,2,0,0,{"wago"},"When Corrupted Blood reaches 25%, a player gains Corruption: Accelerated, which rapidly increases their Corruption level.",-1,0,0,128,167,3223,2,3165,0},
    {3223,"Corruption: Sickness",237514,2,0,0,{"wago"},"When Corrupted Blood reaches 50%, players periodically become violently ill. They vomit and inflict $81831s1 Shadow damage to players within a $81831A1 yard long 20 degree cone in front of them. Players hit by this vile spew suffer increased Corruption.",-1,0,0,0,167,3224,3,3165,0},
    {3224,"Corruption: Malformation",136199,2,0,0,{"wago"},"When Corrupted Blood reaches 75%, the corruption is so thorough that a tentacle Malformation erupts from a player's back. The tentacle periodically casts Shadow Bolts at the player's allies, inflicting $82151s1 Shadow damage.",-1,0,0,0,167,3225,4,3165,0},
    {3225,"Corruption: Absolute",236295,2,0,0,{"wago"},"When Corrupted Blood reaches 100%, players fully transform into faceless horrors. While in this state players cannot be healed, but inflict $82170s2% additional damage and cast spells instantly.",-1,0,0,0,167,0,5,3165,0},
    {3226,"Stage One: I Will Deal With You Myself!",0,0,0,2,{"wago"},"At the outset of the battle, Sinestra is weakened from past battles and from nurturing the Twilight brood. She begins with only 60% of her maximum health, and her damage dealt is reduced by by $89350s1%.",12,3227,0,0,168,3234,1,0,0},
    {3227,"Wrack",132095,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Sinestra causes a random player to suffer Shadow damage every $89421t1 sec. for $89421d. with the damage taken increasing rapidly. When a player dispels Wrack, it bounces to two nearby allies of the afflicted player. Wrack retains its remaining duration but returns to its original damage values.",12,0,0,164,168,3228,2,3226,0},
    {3228,"Flame Breath",135805,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Sinestra unleashes a torrent of flame that sweeps across her platform, inflicting $90125s1 Fire damage to all enemies.",12,0,0,0,168,3229,3,3226,0},
    {3229,"Twilight Slicer",136202,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Sinestra summons two shadowy orbs, each of which fixates on a player and begins to pursue that player. These spheres are linked together by a cutting beam of pure twilight energy that inflicts $92852s1 Shadow damage per $92851t1 sec. to any player who comes into contact with the beam.\n\n\n\nEach sphere also pulses twilight energy, inflicting $92958s1 Shadow damage every $92957t1 sec in a $92958A1 yard radius. The orbs dissipate after $92957d.",12,0,0,48,168,3230,4,3226,0},
    {3230,"Twilight Blast",425959,2,0,2,{"wago"},"When Sinestra cannot reach anyone in melee range, she blasts an enemy for $89280s1 Shadow damage.",12,0,0,0,168,3231,5,3226,0},
    {3231,"Twilight Whelps",0,1,0,2,{"wago"},"Sinestra periodically calls forth a set of five Twilight Whelps to attack intruders.",12,3232,19295,0,168,0,6,3226,0},
    {3232,"Twilight Spit",425954,2,0,2,{"wago"},"The Twilight Whelps spit shadowy bile on their target, inflicting $89299s1 Shadow damage and increasing the target's Shadow damage taken by $89299s2%. This effect stacks.",12,0,0,1,168,3233,7,3231,0},
    {3233,"Twilight Essence",425958,2,0,2,{"wago"},"When a Twilight Whelp dies, the essence instilled in it by Sinestra leaks out, forming a bubbling puddle beneath its corpse. If this essence touches any other dead Twilight Whelp, that Whelp reanimates. Each pool of Twilight Essence expands over time. The pools inflict $88146s2 Shadow damage every $89284t1 sec.",12,0,0,1,168,0,8,3231,0},
    {3234,"Stage Two: I Tire of This!",0,0,0,2,{"wago"},"When Sinestra is brought to 30% health, she draws upon ambient energy to restore her power and erects a shield to protect herself.",12,3235,0,0,168,3245,9,0,0},
    {3235,"A Clash of Flame and Twilight",0,0,0,2,{"wago"},"The red dragon Caelestrasz, Calen in his humanoid form, comes to the party's aid and engages in a magical duel with Sinestra. The duelist with the most mana gains the upper hand.",12,3236,0,0,168,3238,10,3234,0},
    {3236,"Pyrrhic Focus",135817,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Calen burns his own health reserves to restore his mana. His focus also increases healing done to Calen by $87323s2%.",12,0,0,4,168,3237,11,3235,0},
    {3237,"Mana Barrier",136153,2,0,2,{"wago"},"A powerful barrier envelops Sinestra, continually replenishing any lost health at the expense of her mana.",12,0,0,2,168,0,12,3235,0},
    {3238,"Pulsing Twilight Egg",0,1,0,2,{"wago"},"Sinestra has stored vast reserves of twilight energy in these massive eggs.",12,3308,35318,0,168,3239,13,3234,0},
