    {3244,"Absorb Essence",136204,2,0,2,{"wago"},"If a Twilight Drake comes into contact with a pool of Twilight Essence, it siphons that energy and causes the pool to shrink and eventually vanish entirely. Each charge of Essence absorbed increases the Drake's damage by $90107s1%, and its health by $90107s2%. This effect stacks.",12,0,0,1,168,0,20,3242,0},
