    {4129,"Time Zone",136106,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Nozdormu forms a Time Zone at the target location, causing the Elementium Meteor to lapse in time and decrease its travel speed dramatically upon entering the zone. Any enemy creatures within the Time Zone have their attack speed decreased by $105830s1%.$[5,6\n\n\n\nIn Heroic Difficulty the Time Zone slows the effects of Corrupting Parasite.$]",-1,0,0,0,333,0,35,4127,0},
