    {4135,"Spellweaving",135734,2,0,0,{"wago"},"The Presence of Kalecgos allows attacks and abilities to cause Spellweaving. Spellweaving inflicts $106043s2 Arcane damage to enemies within $106043A2 yards, excluding the current target.",-1,0,0,0,333,0,41,4133,0},
