    {4138,"Molten Axe",451168,2,0,2,{"wago"},"The Echo of Baine's Axe ignites for $101836d. when he comes into contact with lava. The fiery axe causes melee attacks to inflict an additional $101840s1 Fire damage.",-2,4139,0,0,340,4140,1,0,0},
