    {4169,"Throw Knife",135430,2,0,3,{"wago"},"Asira throws one of her knives toward a marked enemy spellcaster, inflicting $103597s2 Physical damage to the first player it collides with. If the knife hits a player afflicted with Mark of Silence, it also silences for $103587d.",-14,0,0,32,342,0,2,4167,0},
    {4170,"Choking Smoke Bomb",458733,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Asira creates a cloud of thick smoke in an $103558A1 yard radius around her for $103558d. The cloud prevents enemies from targeting into or out of the smoke cloud and inflicts $103790s2 Nature damage every $103558t2 sec.",-14,0,0,0,342,4171,3,0,0},
    {4171,"Blade Barrier",135642,2,0,2,{"wago"},"At 30% remaining health, Asira begins a dazzling display of weapon mastery. Her Blade Barrier reduces any incoming amount of damage below $103419s1 to 1. The Blade Barrier ends when a player hits Asira with a damaging attack or spell above this threshold.",-14,4175,0,2,342,4168,4,0,0},
    {4172,"Lava Burst",237582,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Thrall hurls molten lava at the target, inflicting $107980s1 Fire damage.",-14,0,0,0,342,4173,7,4168,0},
    {4173,"Rising Fire Totem",135829,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Thrall summons a Fire Totem that periodically increases the damage and maximum health of nearby players. The totem lasts $108374d and its effect can stack up to $103817u times.",-14,0,0,0,342,4174,8,4168,0},
