    {4196,"Degeneration",237530,2,0,0,{"wago"},"The Dreadblade carves a swath of destruction with its dark sword. The sword inflicts $%107558s1 Shadow damage to enemies in a frontal cone, and $%107558s2 Shadow damage every $107558t2 sec for $107558d. This effect stacks.",-1,0,0,1,332,0,12,4194,0},
    {4197,"Twilight Elite Slayer",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,4198,39907,0,332,4200,13,4027,0},
