    {7059,"Overload",237587,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Kazra'jin uses this ability after performing a Reckless Charge while possessed by the spirit of Gara'jal.\n\n\n\nKazra'jin becomes electrified, stunning himself for $137149d and reflecting $137149s1% of all damage taken as Nature damage.",19,0,0,0,816,7060,13,7048,0},
