    {7061,"Sand Bolt",796635,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Sul the Sandcrawler hurls a bolt of sand at a random player's location, inflicting $136190s1 Nature damage to all players within $136190A1 yards of the targeted location.",-1,0,0,64,816,7062,16,7049,0},
