    {7068,"Treacherous Ground",796637,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Quicksand pools that overlap with one another will combine into a single pool of proportionately larger size.\n\n\n\nLiving Sand risen from Quicksand pools that have combined into larger pools have their health and damage increased by $137614s1% for each pool that has combined.",12,0,0,8,816,0,23,7049,0},
