    {7196,"Summon Ball Lightning",839974,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Summon several Ball Lightning elementals at the feet of random targets, inflicting $136543s1 Nature damage to players within $136543A1 yards of each elemental's creation.",-1,7247,0,0,832,7197,19,7192,0},
