    {7886,"Corruption Kick",651098,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Spins rapidly in a circle, rooting himself and inflicting $143009s1 Physical damage to targets within $143009A1 yards every second for $143007D. Additionally torments targets struck, inflicting $143010s1 Shadow damage every two seconds for $143010D.",-1,0,0,0,849,0,17,7888,0},
    {7887,"Corrupted Brew",651085,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Rook Stonetoe hurls a keg of Corrupted Brew at a distant target, inflicting $143023s1 Shadow damage to enemies within $143023A1 yards and slowing targets hit by $143023s2% for $143023d.$[5,6\n\n\n\nIn Heroic difficulty, every two casts, Corrupted Brew's travel time is reduced by half a second. This effect resets when Rook Stonetoe begins his Desperate Measures.$]",-1,0,0,0,849,7888,15,7885,0},
    {7888,"Clash",628134,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Rook Stonetoe clashes against an enemy, charging each other and meeting halfway. Rook Stonetoe then immediately begins to perform Corruption Kick.$[3,4,7,14\n\n\n\nIn Non-Heroic Difficulty, Rook Stonetoe's Clash will not be cast during any Desperate Measures phase.$]",-1,7886,0,0,849,0,16,7885,0},
