    {7907,"Calamity",632353,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Calls forth a great Calamity, striking all players for $143493s1% of their maximum health as Shadow damage. This also removes Shadow Word: Bane from all targets.$[5,6\n\n\n\nIn Heroic difficulty, Calamity increases in magnitude by an additional $143493s2% of maximum health each addtional time it is cast. This effect resets when Sun Tenderheart begins her Desperate Measures.$]$[3,4,7,14\n\n\n\nIn Non-Heroic Difficulty, Sun Tenderheart's Calamity will not be cast during any Desperate Measures phase.$]",-1,0,0,0,849,0,35,7904,0},
