    {7950,"Essence of Y'Shaarj",236296,2,0,2,{"wago"},"The Ancient Miasma forms 2 orbs of corruption every $143846t1 seconds that persist for the remainder of the fight. \n\n\n\nIf a player comes into contact with an orb, it is consumed, removing Ancient Barrier and inflicting $143857s1 Shadow damage to them.$[6\n\n\n\nIn 25-player mode, 5 orbs of corruption are created every $143846t1 sec.$]",12,0,0,8,846,0,3,7872,0},
