    {7956,"Desperate Measures",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"Upon reaching 66% or 33% health remaining, Rook Stonetoe manifests evil forms of his closest friends, making Embodied Misery, Embodied Sorrow, and Embodied Gloom.\n\n\n\nOnce all three spirits are defeated, Rook Stonetoe resumes fighting players.",-1,8395,0,0,849,8145,4,7885,0},
