    {7958,"Defiled Ground",463566,2,0,1,{"wago"},"Embodied Misery smashes the ground with fervor, inflicting $143961s1 Physical damage to her current target, knocking them back. This force burns into the ground, inflicting $144357s1 Shadow damage every second.",-1,0,0,0,849,0,6,8395,0},
