    {8416,"Prelude: Clear the Landing",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"The naval ships cannot land while the beachfront is still fortified with cannons. Take out the cannons to secure the landing.",-1,0,0,0,868,8417,1,0,0},
    {8417,"Phase 1: Bring Her Down!",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"Warlord Zaela sends her finest Dragonmaw soldiers to battle. Two guardians keep watch over the Towers above, protecting the Anti-Air turrets. Defeating these guardians will give players access to the Anti-Air turrets.\n\n\n\nTwo well-timed Anti-Air turret shots will send Galakras spiraling towards the ground.",-1,8421,0,0,868,8418,2,0,0},
