    {8429,"Dragonmaw Flameslinger",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"These deadly archers shoot fire-tipped arrows at random players. The effect inflicts Fire damage on impact, and then burns the ground and any players standing within.",-1,0,50970,0,868,8430,23,8427,0},
