    {8445,"Crusher's Call",463560,2,0,0,{"wago"},"High Enforcer Thranok lashes out with chains, hooking 5 random players within $146769A1 yards and pulls them to his feet. $[4, 6, 7\n\n\n\nIn 25 player mode, High Enforcer Thranok hooks 10 random players.$]\n\n\n\nAfterwards, Thranok rears back to execute his savage attack, Skull Cracker, that inflicts $146848s2 Physical damage to all players within $146848A2 yards.",-1,0,0,16,868,0,12,8424,0},
