    {8470,"Caustic Blood",132105,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Successful melee strikes from Xaril inject a caustic poison into the victim. The injection inflicts $142315s1 Nature damage per application to the target every second for $142315d. If the injection is allowed to stack to 10, a Bloody Explosion occurs.\n\n\n\nCaustic Blood will fail to hit tanks who are using their Active Mitigation abilities.",-1,8471,0,1,853,8035,45,8009,0},
