    {8473,"Faulty Mutation",878216,2,0,2,{"wago"},"In Heroic Difficulties, mutated victims suffer a Faulty Mutation. If the victim fails to Prey on an Amber Parasite before the Faulty Mutation expires they will perish.",12,0,0,24,853,0,21,8472,0},
